                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18350302-826-offence-1 t18350302-cd-127"></join>18th of Feb<lb></lb>ruary</rs>, 8 handkerchiefs, value 30<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18350302-name-895" type="victimName">
