                        <interp inst="t18350302-name-898" type="given" value="ARTHUR"></interp>ARTHUR MINTON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 80.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction, which I got at Mr. Clark's office (<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—I know the prisoner is the person.</p>
               <p>(Mr. King, master of the British School, Golden-lane, gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
